Statistical analysis using p-values and chi-square values (Optional)¶

Please note:¶

For the below statements you need to state the Null and Alternate and then provide a statistical test to accept or reject the Null Hypothesis along with the corresponding ‘p-value’.

a. Whether the average response time across complaint types is similar or not (overall)¶

b. Are the type of complaint or service requested and location related?¶

H0: Null Hypothesis: Average response time across complaint types is similar(overall). H1: Alternate Hypothesis: Average response time across complaint types is not similar(overall).

Testing for our Hypothesis¶

For relation between Complaint Type and Location¶

we will use Crosstab and Chi-square Test
